1\/care-for-orphans-free-slaves\/","url_meta":{"origin":7733,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Orphans: Care for the orphans, free the slaves","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 11, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Malik ibn Al-Harith reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever embraces an orphan of two Muslim parents by feeding him and giving him drink until he is independent of him, Paradise will certainly be necessary for him. Whoever emancipates a Muslim man, he will\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19025,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/07\/allah-provides-sadaqah-miskin\/","url_meta":{"origin":7733,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Poor: Allah supports by charity to weak","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 7, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Mus\u2019ab ibn Sa\u2019d reported: Sa\u2019d viewed himself as better than those below him. The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said to him, \u201cAre you not\u00a0given support and provision due to your vulnerable ones?\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2896 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0635\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0628\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24280,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/01\/22\/funeral-good-witness\/","url_meta":{"origin":7733,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Funerals: Muslims whose good is witnessed enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhenever four persons testify to the goodness of a Muslim, he will enter Paradise.\u201d We said, \u201cAnd three?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cEven three.\u201d We said, \u201cAnd two?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cEven two.\u201d Thereafter, we did not ask\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18973,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/03\/gossiper-not-enter-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":7733,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Namimah: Gossip-monger will not enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 3, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe gossiper will not enter Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6056, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 105 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064f\u0630\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u062f\u0652\u062e\u064f\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u062a\u0651\u064e\u0627\u062a\u064c 6056 \u0635\u062d\u064a\u062d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32182,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/avoid-seven-mortal-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":7733,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sins: Avoid seven major sins, idolatry, killing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cStay away from seven mortal sins.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are they?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIdolatry with Allah, occult magic, killing a soul that Allah has sanctified except for a just cause, consuming usury, usurping\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33708,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/13\/former-enemies-embrace-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":7733,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Da&#8217;wah: Former enemies, prisoners embrace Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah marvels at people who enter Paradise in chains.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3010 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari Ibn al-Jawzi said, \u201cIt means they are taken prisoner and detained, but when they recognize the rightness of Islam,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7733","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=7733"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7733\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=7733"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=7733"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=7733"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}